OL,3,CPlan for a merger of councils in
OL,4,CStaffordshire divides opinion
OL,6,FStoke-on-Trent City Council has
OL,7,Fannounced it is backing a plan for a
OL,8,Flarge North Staffordshire Council.
OL,10,FThe government has pushed for a
OL,11,Freorganisation of local authorities,
OL,12,Fwhich would see the replacement of
OL,13,Fsmaller councils like boroughs and
OL,14,Fdistricts with a single-tier of larger
OL,15,Fones.
OL,17,FThe plans in Staffordshire would see
OL,18,Fthe merging of Stoke-on-Trent,
OL,19,FStaffordshire Moorlands and Newcastle-
OL,20,Funder-Lyme's authorities.
