OL,3,CPlan for a merger of councils in
OL,4,CStaffordshire divides opinion
OL,6,FThe plans are part of the biggest
OL,7,Fshake up of local government in
OL,8,Fdecades, which is largely a cost-
OL,9,Fsaving measure. But they have been met
OL,10,Fwith criticism from councillors in
OL,11,Fsmaller administrations.
OL,13,FCouncillor Jane Ashworth, the Leader
OL,14,Fof Stoke on Trent City Council, said
OL,15,Fshe's backing the plan for a 'super-
OL,16,Fsized' local authority, saying it
OL,17,Fwould be good for economic growth and
OL,18,Fwould benefit local services.
