OL,3,CPlan for a merger of councils in
OL,4,CStaffordshire divides opinion
OL,6,FBut the proposals have also been met
OL,7,Fwith fierce criticism, including from
OL,8,FCouncillor Simon Tagg, Leader of
OL,9,FNewcastle-Under-Lyme Borough Council,
OL,10,Fwho fears that the unique identity of
OL,11,Feach area will disappear if they are
OL,12,Fmerged as one.
OL,14,FHe said: "What the city council have
OL,15,Fput forward is no benefit to my
OL,16,Fresidents. What we have at the moment
OL,17,Fis a low council tax here in
OL,18,FNewcastle, with 1.99%.
