OL,3,CPlan for a merger of councils in
OL,4,CStaffordshire divides opinion
OL,6,F"We provide good local services that
OL,7,Fpeople can see and use everyday, and
OL,8,Fwhat we do see is a he city council
OL,9,Fthat is debt, it's having to take its
OL,10,Fschools to court and also it has got
OL,11,Ftrouble with its children's services
OL,12,Fso I don't think it will be of any
OL,13,Fbenefit to our residents here in
OL,14,FNewcastle."
OL,16,FITV News Central asked people living
OL,17,Fin the village of Blythe Bridge, which
OL,18,Fis eight miles from Stoke-on-Trent,
OL,19,Fwhat they thought of the proposals.
