OL,3,CPlan for a merger of councils in
OL,4,CStaffordshire divides opinion
OL,6,FOne resident said it would be
OL,7,F"disappointing" to see the devolution
OL,8,Fplans come to fruition.
OL,10,F"I think there would be too many
OL,11,Fdecisions made on a wider basis and it
OL,12,Fwould have a big impact on local areas
OL,13,Flike libraries for example."
OL,15,FAnother said: "I'm certainly not happy
OL,16,Fwith the way things are, but I don't
OL,17,Fthink that evolving power upwards is
OL,18,Fgoing to be the remedy."
