OL,6,FAnother added: "It would be better if
OL,7,Fthey worked together. It would save
OL,8,Fconfusion on who does what jobs. I
OL,9,Fthink it would work better."
OL,11,F"You can still keep your local Parish
OL,12,FCouncils but an overall responsibility
OL,13,Ffor me would be better for budgeting",
OL,14,Fanother said.
